import React from 'react'
import Navbaar from '../Navbaar'
import Footer from '../Footer'
import Contact from '../Contact'

function Contacts() {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbaar/>
      <Contact/>
      <Footer />
    </>
  )
}
export default Contacts
